        "creation_date": 1456385880,
        "body": "<p>The easiest that comes to my mind is requiring a single <code>Options<\/code> paramenter in the <code>Parent<\/code> constructor and set default values in that options type:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>public class Parent {\n  public Parent(Options options) {\n    // ...\n  }\n}\n\n// Default values set here\npublic class Options {\n  public int someInt = 42;\n  public String someString = \"Hello world!\";\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
